WEBVTT

00:00:02.864 --> 00:00:03.824
Tension headaches

00:00:03.820 --> 00:00:04.984
are one of the most common

00:00:04.980 --> 00:00:06.696
types of headache in adults.

00:00:06.984 --> 00:00:08.352
Pain is usually felt on

00:00:08.350 --> 00:00:09.664
both sides of the head,

00:00:09.660 --> 00:00:10.816
at the temples or

00:00:10.810 --> 00:00:12.168
back of the head and neck.

00:00:12.544 --> 00:00:14.072
Some people say it feels like

00:00:14.070 --> 00:00:15.816
your head is in a vice.

00:00:16.088 --> 00:00:18.096
Tension headaches do not throb.

00:00:18.090 --> 00:00:20.264
The pain can last from 30 minutes

00:00:20.260 --> 00:00:21.824
to several days.

00:00:21.820 --> 00:00:23.968
It may be relieved by relaxing

00:00:23.960 --> 00:00:26.392
or taking a nonprescription pain reliever.

00:00:26.656 --> 00:00:28.696
 Fifteen or more tension headaches

00:00:28.690 --> 00:00:30.360
a month for several months

00:00:30.360 --> 00:00:31.720
is considered a chronic

00:00:31.720 --> 00:00:32.992
tension headache and a

00:00:32.990 --> 00:00:35.312
physician can prescribe treatment.

